<L>__{interior craft service table. day}
<A>__{several members of the crew loiter around the table. the scriptgirl approaches carrying a donut in one hand and a cup of coffee in the other. palomino notices her and moves quietly to her side. without a word he picks up the milk and pours some in her coffee. nicole stands nearby and watches the following exchange.}
<C>__{script}
<D>__{thanks.}
<C>__{palomino}
<D>__{my pleasure. sugar?}
<C>__{script}
<D>__{just a bit.}
<A>__{palomino puts sugar in her coffee with extreme care.}
